column5: Can someone give an update on teh water level on the Woods? Thanks
It's gotta be at least a foot and a half above the maps.
So motoring into obabikon is no problem?
It looks to be something over a foot higher than what it was last Sep. See http://www.lwcb.ca/pdf/lakeofthewood...2009.05.26.pdf Bill Krejca
just back from Morson area. Water a foot higher than last fall when it was no problem getting through. Lots of current but shouldn't be a problem. Fishing was incredible!
no problem at all getting into Obabikon.
